<bibRefCitation author="Burckhardt D." box="[189,398,1996,2022]" pageId="28" pageNumber="165" pagination="299 - 392" refId="ref20886" refString="Burckhardt D. 1987. Jumping plant lice (Homoptera: Psylloidea) of the temperate Neotropical region. Part 1: Psyllidae (subfamilies Aphalarinae, Rhinocolinae and Aphalaroidinae). Zoological Journal of the Linnean Society 89: 299 - 392. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1096 - 3642.1987. tb 01568. x" type="journal article" year="1987">Burckhardt, 1987</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[409,538,1995,2022]" pageId="28" pageNumber="165">A, C, E, G</emphasis>
. Habitus, in profile view. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[842,965,1996,2022]" pageId="28" pageNumber="165">B, D, F, H</emphasis>
